{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd25 <strong>IF YOU LIKE THE GAME, PLEASE WISHLIST</strong> \ud83d\udd25<br>You'll get notified when we launch the demo and it helps us reach more players! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Drakontias</strong> is an illustrated text-based RPG with deep branching narrative and card battles. Explore the mystical realm of Aldunia where every choice you make, shapes the story. <i>Will you revive the dragon-god Drakontias or claim his power for yourself?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/p.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Section-Choices-v2.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world of Aldunia reacts to your actions, ensuring no two playthroughs are the same.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-MakeChoices.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a deep branching narrative, your choices have far-reaching consequences and can lead to different paths, alliances, and endings.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-BranchingDialogs.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/p.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Section-Battle-v2.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in tactical card battles that require strategy and foresight. Mastering your deck is key to surviving the dangers that lie ahead.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-Fight.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect powerful hand-painted cards, pace your Stamina, and build your deck to suit your playstyle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-Deck.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/p.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Section-Explore-v2.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the last Keeper, your mission is to gather the shattered essence of the dragon-god Drakontias, whose power once maintained the balance of the world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-Artifact.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore diverse landscapes, from ancient forests to frozen lakes, scorching deserts and desolate ruins, each brought to life with stunning hand-painted illustrations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-Explore.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter a wide range of characters and bizarre creatures, each with their own stories, and decide their fate with your choices. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-Power.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Will you restore Drakontias to his former glory, or seize his power for your own ambitions? The fate of Aldunia is in your hands.</i> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/p.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Section-Developer-v2.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-Enchantress.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We\u2019re a 2-people indie studio from Vancouver \ud83c\udde8\ud83c\udde6 with a passion for storytelling and beautiful art. <strong>Drakontias</strong> is our first indie game, born from a deep passion and nostalgia for the 90's pen-and-paper gamebooks \u2014 <i>Fighting Fantasy</i>, <i>Sorcery!</i>, <i>Lone Wolf</i>, <i>Metamorphose</i> \u2014 and inspired by titles like \u2014 <i>Skyrim</i>, <i>Slay the Spire</i>, <i>Roadwarden</i>, <i>80 Days</i>. Our goal is to blend compelling writing, branching narratives, stunning landscapes, rich RPG mechanics, and thrilling card battles into an experience that players will love!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Thank you for your support!</strong> \u2764\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u2013 Leo Sanders, Founder of Spark Machine</i><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/p.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Title.png?t=1738532384\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2489720?t=1738532384","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738532384","capsule_image":"https://shar