9720/extras/Drakontias-Explore.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter a wide range of characters and bizarre creatures, each with their own stories, and decide their fate with your choices. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-Power.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Will you restore Drakontias to his former glory, or seize his power for your own ambitions? The fate of Aldunia is in your hands.</i> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/p.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Section-Developer-v2.png?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/Drakontias-Enchantress.gif?t=1738532384\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We\u2019re a 2-people indie studio from Vancouver \ud83c\udde8\ud83c\udde6 with a passion for storytelling and beautiful art. <strong>Drakontias</strong> is our first indie game, born from a deep passion and nostalgia for the 90's pen-and-paper gamebooks \u2014 <i>Fighting Fantasy</i>, <i>Sorcery!</i>, <i>Lone Wolf</i>, <i>Metamorphose</i> \u2014 and inspired by titles like \u2014 <i>Skyrim</i>, <i>Slay the Spire</i>, <i>Roadwarden</i>, <i>80 Days</i>. Our goal is to blend compelling writing, branching narratives, stunning landscapes, rich RPG mechanics, and thrilling card battles into an experience that players will love!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Thank you for your support!</strong> \u2764\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u2013 Leo Sanders, Founder of Spark Machine</i><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489720/extras/p